<br>
I knew this was coming from his posts but I always held out hope that he would play every once in a while. <br>
<br>
He is the kind of person you could always count on. Fiercely loyal to his friends and unswerving in his beliefs.<br>
<br>
 I always looked forward to talking with him in game even if we weren't hunting together. <br>
<br>
